OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed for a number
OL,7,Fof serious sexual offences against a
OL,8,Fvulnerable girl in the 1990s in
OL,9,FDewsbury and Ossett.
OL,11,FShe told police she had been sexually
OL,12,Fexploited by multiple offenders when
OL,13,Fshe was a child which began the
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FThe court heard the young girl stopped
OL,17,Fregularly attending school after she
OL,18,Fwas introduced to groups of older
OL,19,Fteenage boys and adult men.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
