PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FShe said her childhood was
OL,7,Fsignificantly affected after she was
OL,8,Fsupplied with alcohol and sexual
OL,9,Foffending against her began when she
OL,10,Fwas between 13 and 17 years old.
OL,12,FThe offences took place between 1994
OL,13,Fand 1999.
OL,15,FZahid Hussain, 48, was the first man
OL,16,Fto sexually assault her. During a
OL,17,Fparty, he pulled her by her hair into
OL,18,Fa room and then forced her to perform
OL,19,Foral sex on him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
