FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FThe offending continued at multiple
OL,7,Flocations. He was jailed for 10 years
OL,8,Fand six months after a trial of six
OL,9,Fcounts of indecent assault.
OL,11,FMohammed Chhibda forced her to perform
OL,12,Foral sex on him while they were in a
OL,13,Fparked vehicle. The 49-year-old was
OL,14,Fconvicted of two counts of indecent
OL,15,Fassault and jailed for 11 years.
OL,17,FBasharat Wali, who was also older,
OL,18,Fmade her perform oral sex on him. He
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,20,Fto two counts of sexual assault and
OL,21,Fwas jailed for 12 months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
