CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FWhen she was 16 and 17 years old, she
OL,7,Fmet Jagtar Sahota who was 20 years
OL,8,Folder than her.
OL,10,FShe was working at one of Mr Sahota's
OL,11,Ftakeaway businesses, where she was
OL,12,Fisolated and vulnerable, having
OL,13,Falready suffered sexual exploitation
OL,14,Fby other men.
OL,16,FMr Sahota paid her more than other
OL,17,Femployees and developed a pattern of
OL,18,Fbehaviour in which he subjected her to
OL,19,Frepeated nonconsensual sexual
OL,20,Factivity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
