FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FThe abuse included multiple serious
OL,7,Fsexual assaults, including rape and
OL,8,Fsexual assaults by penetration. The
OL,9,Foffences took place at commercial and
OL,10,Fresidential premises connected to Mr
OL,11,FSahota, as well as in motor vehicles,
OL,12,Fbetween 1997 and 2000.
OL,14,FMr Sahota was found guilty of 23
OL,15,Fcounts at an earlier trial and he was
OL,16,Fsentenced at Leeds Crown Court to 21
OL,17,Fyears imprisonment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
