FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,FIn a statement for the court, the
OL,7,Fsurvivor said: "I was so young, so
OL,8,Fvulnerable, and they knew exactly what
OL,9,Fthey were doing. They didn't care that
OL,10,FI was a child. They didn't care that I
OL,11,Fdidn't understand. They used me,
OL,12,Fabused me then discarded me.
OL,14,F"They took pieces of my soul, pieces
OL,15,Fof my body, pieces of me that I will
OL,16,Fnever get back. They made sure I would
OL,17,Fnever be the same again," she
OL,18,Fcontinued.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,F"The worst part was the abuse didn't
OL,7,Fstop when it ended. It never ends.
OL,8,FEvery time I go into a bathroom or
OL,9,Fhear certain music played in a car,
OL,10,Fthe fear and memories flood back like
OL,11,Fa tidal wave."
OL,13,FJulia McSorley, Specialist Prosecutor
OL,14,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service's
OL,15,FOrganised Child Sexual Abuse Unit,
OL,16,Fsaid the defendants deliberately
OL,17,Ftargeted the victim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
