OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780665075
OL,3,CMen jailed for serious sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst vulnerable girl in the 1990s
OL,6,F"These perpetrators of sexual abuse
OL,7,Fall deliberately targeted this victim,
OL,8,Fbecause she was younger, and
OL,9,Fvulnerable, in the selfish pursuit of
OL,10,Ftheir own sexual gratification.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank her for her
OL,13,Fexceptional courage in giving evidence
OL,14,Fand securing the convictions of the
OL,15,Fmen responsible for these offences."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
